      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Follow this advice if you’re a:</p>

<ul>
  <li>post-16 further education (<abbr title="further education">FE</abbr>) provider</li>
  <li>
<abbr title="further education">FE</abbr> college</li>
  <li>sixth form college</li>
  <li>other <abbr title="further education">FE</abbr> provider</li>
</ul>

<p>The advice explains what you’ll need to do during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak to maintain provision.</p>

</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

